textAfterTable: (1) Limited Edition SUP Company TD49 Signature Black Stand Up Paddle board 11'2" with fin, deck pad and 2 extra fins for surfing. This Signature board Series model reflects the paddling and SUP surfing style of SUPCO owner and founder, Tommy Donnelly. The PVC foam layer gives the board a lighter weight making it easy to maneuver while paddling or surfing. With a round pin tail and tri-fin set up, this board will give you a lot of drive and turning on a wave. Extra length also supplies more stability for the bigger paddler. Features: Tri-fin set up, fingure contour grip. Construction: EPS foam core, reinforced sealed rails, nose and tail, dual layers of 4 oz. fiberglass cloth with epoxy resin and a PVC foam layer.  Great condition.  Normal wear for a few times used.
